# Test your FastAPI endpoints

# Basic health check
GET http://127.0.0.1:8000/health
Accept: application/json

###

# Liveness/Readiness check
GET http://127.0.0.1:8000/healthz
Accept: application/json

###

# Comprehensive health check with all services
GET http://127.0.0.1:8000/health/services/s3
Accept: application/json

###

GET http://127.0.0.1:8000/health/services/models
Accept: application/json

###

GET http://127.0.0.1:8000/health/services/minio
Accept: application/json

###

GRPC localhost:8080/mlservice.HealthService/Check